{"data":{"markdownRemark":null,"npmPackage":{"name":"gatsby-source-anilist","description":"Gatsby source plugin for building websites using the AniList GraphQL API as a data source","keywords":["gatsby","gatsby-plugin","gatsby-source-plugin"],"lastPublisher":{"name":"jamesdanylik","avatar":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/9b3c60cd4c68ed005185c60b6d80479e"},"modified":"2018-05-29T01:31:15.702Z","repository":{"url":"https://github.com/jamesdanylik/gatsby-source-anilist"},"readme":{"childMarkdownRemark":{"html":"<h1 id=\"gatsby-source-anilist\"><a href=\"#gatsby-source-anilist\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>gatsby-source-anilist</h1>\n<p>This is a Gatsby source plugin to pull data from the <a href=\"https://github.com/AniList/ApiV2-GraphQL-Docs\">Anilist GraphQL API</a>.  It is heavily based on the excellent <a href=\"https://github.com/DSchau/gatsby-source-github\">gatsby-source-github</a> (which I aslo use and cannot recommend enough) by <a href=\"https://github.com/DSchau\">Dustin Schau</a>, who as far as I know came up with this stategy of connecting graphql databases.  I modified this technique to work with the Anilist API with minimal changes.</p>\n<h1 id=\"install\"><a href=\"#install\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Install</h1>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\">\n      <pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">npm</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> gatsby-source-anilist --save-dev</code></pre>\n      </div>\n<h1 id=\"usage\"><a href=\"#usage\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Usage</h1>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\">\n      <pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// In your gatsby-config.js</span>\nplugins<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t  resolve<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'gatsby-source-anilist'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\t  options<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t    queries<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n\t      <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`\n\t        {\n\t          MediaListCollection(userId: 122315, type:ANIME) {\n\t            lists {\n\t              name\n\t              entries {\n\t                id\n\t                media {\n\t                  id\n\t                  title {\n\t                    romaji\n\t                    english\n\t                    native\n\t                    userPreferred\n\t                  }\n\t                }\n\t              }\n\t              isCustomList\n\t              isSplitCompletedList\n\t              status\n\t            }\n\t          }\n\t        }\n\t      `</span></span>\n\t    <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n\t  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\t<span class=\"token operator\">...</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span></code></pre>\n      </div>\n<p>Where queries is an array of valid graphql queries for Anilist.  These can be tested live in <a href=\"https://anilist.co/graphiql\">AniList’s GraphQL Explorer</a>.</p>\n<h1 id=\"querying-data\"><a href=\"#querying-data\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Querying Data</h1>\n<p>Returned results are added to Gatsby’s GraphQL nodes with the renaming convention from the original gatsby-source-gtihub.  <a href=\"https://github.com/DSchau/gatsby-source-github#the-algorithm\">See David’s description here</a> for more information.</p>\n<h1 id=\"example\"><a href=\"#example\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Example</h1>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\">\n      <pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  resolve<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'gatsby-source-anilist'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  options<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    queries<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n      <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`\n        {\n          MediaListCollection(userId: 122315, type:ANIME) {\n            lists {\n              name\n              entries {\n                id\n                media {\n                  id\n                  title {\n                    romaji\n                    english\n                    native\n                    userPreferred\n                  }\n                }\n              }\n              isCustomList\n              isSplitCompletedList\n              status\n            }\n          }\n        }\n      `</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span></code></pre>\n      </div>\n<p>Produces:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\">\n      <pre class=\"language-graphql\"><code class=\"language-graphql\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  allAnilistMedialistcollection <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    edges <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      node <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        id\n        lists <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n          name\n          entries <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n            media <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n              id\n              title <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n                romaji\n                english\n                native\n                userPreferred\n              <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n            <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n          <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n          isCustomList\n          isSplitCompletedList\n          status\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre>\n      </div>","timeToRead":1}}}},"pathContext":{"slug":"/packages/gatsby-source-anilist/","id":"b050be9a-3637-56f7-9868-e15fb982ee37"}}